  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Ghoran&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Past-Life Knowledge, Nature Magic&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Many ghorans are resistant to magic or able to dispel it. Some ghorans even gain nourishment from absorbing magic. Whenever such a ghoran succeeds at a saving throw against a spell or spell-like ability, she regains 1 hit point per level of the spell, though this affects the ghoran only if she is above 0 hit points. A ghoran can use this ability a number of times per day equal to her level. This replaces past-life knowledge and nature magic.</p>",
